THREE dangerous prisoners are on the run! They escaped from Middledrift Prison in the Eastern Cape on Tuesday. Police and correctional services have launched a manhunt. They are looking for: Correctional services spokeswoman Nobuntu Gantana said: “Circumstances leading to their escape aren’t yet known, but criminal and internal investigations are under way to see if they were assisted to escape. “The three offenders are dangerous. Those who see them shouldn’t try to catch them. People are urged to report any information they have to their nearest police station. “The department is doing everything in its power to rearrest the escapees. We’re committed to ensuring all citizens feel safe.”